items.summary: Create a Privacy Policy page accessible at /privacy route that displays privacy policy content in a clean, readable format consistent with the construction-themed design using the existing orange/charcoal/safety yellow color palette

Create a Terms of Service page accessible at /terms route that displays terms of service content in a clean, readable format consistent with the construction-themed design using the existing orange/charcoal/safety yellow color palette

Create a Support page accessible at /support route that provides contact information and help resources in a clean, readable format consistent with the construction-themed design using the existing orange/charcoal/safety yellow color palette
Add navigation links to Privacy, Terms, and Support pages in the footer section of the Landing page so users can access these pages before authentication
